Dear [Expert],

We are conducting a Delphi study to validate a proposed Logistics Readiness Level (LRL) scale for planetary-scale engineering projects, specifically for Mars Partial Planetary Engineering (PPE). Your expertise in [systems engineering / aerospace / history of technology] would be invaluable.

The study involves three rounds of online questionnaires, each taking approximately 30–45 minutes. Your responses will be anonymized, and you will have the opportunity to revise your judgments based on group feedback. The results will contribute to a PhD thesis and potentially to future NASA/ESA planning.

If you are willing to participate, please reply to this email. We will send you the Round 1 materials upon confirmation.

Thank you for considering.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]

